          "type": "paragraph",
          "settings": {
            "text": "Wellie Bellie Bites are expertly formulated to support your dog’s gut health. If you’ve noticed tear stains in their eyes, a dull coat, your dog scratching itself, licking its paws, or just bad breath that doesn’t seem to go away - the Bellie Bites are the answer to these common issues.  "
