        },
        "paragraph_HD7pCL": {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "settings": {
            "text": "Our premium supplements are designed to optimize digestive health, enhance immune function, and improve overall well-being. Powered by a scientifically developed blend of prebiotics, probiotics, and digestive enzymes, each treat delivers targeted benefits for a healthier, happier pet. "
          }
        },
        "paragraph_jbag49": {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "settings": {
            "text": "Each of these bites comes with 4 billion CFUs - that’s 4 Billion clinically approved live strains to help your dog build good bacteria and defend against allergies."
          }
        }
